RISK VS REWARD tracked the leaders between horses through the early going, saved ground around the turn and kept on in the lane. SIR AGGRAVATOR chased the leaders on the inside up the backstretch, saved ground around the turn and faded in the lane.

TAKESTWOTOWIGGLE led the way on the outside racing up the backstretch, dropped back from the three path coming around the turn and continued to tire in the lane.
